OL,3,CJersey politicians vote to keep trans
OL,4,Cinclusive school guidance
OL,6,FNew guidance on how children who are
OL,7,Fquestioning their gender should be
OL,8,Ftreated in schools has been rejected
OL,9,Fby the States of Jersey.
OL,11,FSir Deputy Philip Bailhache lodged the
OL,12,Fproposition - called 'Treating
OL,13,FChildren as Children' - which would
OL,14,Fhave advised schools and teachers to
OL,15,Ftake a "neutral" and "watching,
OL,16,Fwaiting approach" to gender-
OL,17,Fquestioning students.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
