PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1774559156
OL,3,CJersey politicians vote to keep trans
OL,4,Cinclusive school guidance
OL,6,FThe politician called Jersey's
OL,7,Fexisting policy "flawed", arguing that
OL,8,Fparents should be told if their
OL,9,Fchildren were questioning their gender
OL,10,Fat school, unless there were
OL,11,Fsafeguarding concerns.
OL,13,FHowever, after the debate ran into
OL,14,Fanother day, just five politicians
OL,15,Fvoted pour (for) Sir Bailhache's
OL,16,Fproposition, with 35 contre (against).
OL,18,FFive abstained, and four were absent
OL,19,Ffor voting.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
