OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1774559157
OL,3,CJersey politicians vote to keep trans
OL,4,Cinclusive school guidance
OL,6,FAt the opening of the debate on
OL,7,FTuesday afternoon (24 March), Deputy
OL,8,FBailhache said he had spoken directly
OL,9,Fto students who were concerned with
OL,10,Fhis proposition.
OL,12,FThe politician told the States that
OL,13,Fwhile he supported transgender adults
OL,14,Fand their freedom to choose their
OL,15,Fgender identities, he had reservations
OL,16,Fabout the current guidance, which he
OL,17,Fdescribed as "muddled and
OL,18,Fcontradictory".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1774559157
OL,3,CJersey politicians vote to keep trans
OL,4,Cinclusive school guidance
OL,6,FDeputy Bailhache also claimed that
OL,7,Faffirming a child's desire to socially
OL,8,Ftransition would likely push them to
OL,9,Fpursue medical treatment later in life.
OL,11,FHowever, Deputy Rob Ward, Jersey's
OL,12,FMinister for Education, told the
OL,13,FStates that the proposal had "serious
OL,14,Fflaws", including language that could
OL,15,Fbe regarded as "harmful or
OL,16,Fdiscriminatory against children".
OL,18,FDeputy Ward also claimed that the
OL,19,Fframework for the proposition was
OL,20,F"authored externally" by pressure
OL,21,Fgroups from the UK.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1774559157
OL,3,CJersey politicians vote to keep trans
OL,4,Cinclusive school guidance
OL,6,F"Every pupil should feel safe and be
OL,7,Ftreated with respect," the Minister
OL,8,Ffor Education told the States Chamber.
OL,9,F"The document suggested is not child-
OL,10,Fcentred safeguarding. It is a
OL,11,Fpolitical doctrine presented as
OL,12,Fguidance. The position leans on UK
OL,13,Flegal positions and advocacy claims
OL,14,Fthat do not map to Jersey.
OL,16,F"The (current) document already states
OL,17,Fa watch-and-wait, case-by-case
OL,18,Fsupport, and that medical decisions
OL,19,Fare outside the school.
OL,26,@xD@FpmxD@Npn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1774559157
OL,3,CJersey politicians vote to keep trans
OL,4,Cinclusive school guidance
OL,6,F"If Members have genuine concerns
OL,7,Flinked to the guidance in schools,
OL,8,Fthere are practical improvements we
OL,9,Fcan create and support without
OL,10,Foverturning departmental guidance in
OL,11,Ffavour of an external manifesto."
OL,13,FFollowing the debate, Deputy Bailhache
OL,14,Ftold ITV News he was "disappointed"
OL,15,Fwith the outcome.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1774559157
OL,3,CJersey politicians vote to keep trans
OL,4,Cinclusive school guidance
OL,6,F"The guidance of the education
OL,7,Fdepartment is apparently going to be
OL,8,Freviewed in 2027, and I very much hope
OL,9,Fthat when that review takes place,
OL,10,Fmany of the issues that were raised
OL,11,Fduring the course of this debate will
OL,12,Fbe seriously considered and taken into
OL,13,Faccount.
OL,15,F"I think it was important to bring
OL,16,Fforward the proposition because there
OL,17,Fare serious issues about how one
OL,18,Fshould treat gender-questioning
OL,19,Fchildren, which are not being
OL,20,Faddressed at the moment."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1774559157
OL,3,CJersey politicians vote to keep trans
OL,4,Cinclusive school guidance
OL,6,FDeputy Louise Doublet, who voted
OL,7,Fagainst the proposition, believes the
OL,8,FStates Assembly gave proposals "due
OL,9,Fconsideration", adding that the
OL,10,Fcurrent guidance is "reasonable" for
OL,11,Fschoolchildren.
OL,13,F"It's not one single pathway, it's
OL,14,Fsomething that relies on the good
OL,15,Fjudgement of teachers and has
OL,16,Fsafeguarding at its core, and I'm
OL,17,Fpleased that the States Assembly made
OL,18,Fthat sensible decision.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1774559157
OL,3,CJersey politicians vote to keep trans
OL,4,Cinclusive school guidance
OL,6,F"I know that some people have felt
OL,7,Fvulnerable in terms of listening to
OL,8,Fthe rhetoric around this debate, and I
OL,9,Fthink what we've shown today is that
OL,10,FJersey is a place that is
OL,11,Fcompassionate and inclusive.
OL,13,F"Those are our Jersey values, and we
OL,14,Fmust continue to protect those values."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/9
